com.example.katrin.testsnepet

Class EloScores2

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.katrin.testsnepet.EloScores2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class EloScores2
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Stores the ELO scores from a user in a float array. Implements Parcelable to enable the passing on of the data through intent. However, due to unmarshalling error this class is not in use at the moment.
    Version:
    1.0, 5 jun 2018
    Author:
    Rick Dijkstra
